meta {
  name: Subscribe Fiat Rates
  type: ws
  seq: 4
}

ws {
  url: wss://bitcoin-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/{{api_key}}
  body: ws
  auth: inherit
}

body:ws {
  name: subscribe
  type: json
  content: '''
    {
      "id": "4",
      "method": "subscribeFiatRates",
      "params": {
        "currency": "usd"
      }
    }
  '''
}

docs {
  Emits an event when the fiat rate ticker for the chain's native asset updates.

  Parameters:
  - currency (string, optional) - Filter to a single fiat currency (e.g. "usd", "eur"). When omitted, the server emits all available currencies on each update.

  On subscribe, returns a confirmation that the subscription is active. Subsequent events include updated fiat rates for the requested currency or currencies.

  https://www.alchemy.com/docs/bitcoin/utxo-websockets#subscribefiatrates
}
